PCR Simulation
==============

NOTE:
	MUST BE BUILT IN LINUX
	MUST BE BUILT ON A COMPUTER WHICH HAS GCC 4.8

Setup:
To install primer3 for your project, run the following commands:
	> cd <path_to_repo>/PCR/
	> tar xvfz primer3-src-2.3.6.tar.gz
	> cd primer3-2.3.6/src/
	> make all

To compile the project:
		In the directory of the project:
			
		> make
		
To run the project:
		./PCR [SEQUENCE FILE] [START POSITION] [END POSITION] [CYCLES OF PCR TO RUN]
		
		Example:
		./PCR sequence.txt 100 500 20
